had formed numerous alliances with powerful  

21
00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:22.320
families and clans, introducing skilled people 
to elites, helping many influencing people  

22
00:02:22.320 --> 00:02:28.080
rise to power and stabilizing the rule of the 
shogunate during hard times. I hope this still  

23
00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:33.840
yields fruitfully and people still believe in the 
